        "created_at": "2015-12-30T04:44:18.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>About 25 miles from SA is a pretty good one\u2026<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.drycomalcreek.com/\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">http://www.drycomalcreek.com/</a></p>\n<p>I went to a wedding just behind the vineyard, and swung by the tasting room. Pretty cool for a Louisiana boy. I remember the soil was very stony\u2026</p>",
