        "created_at": "2015-12-30T19:56:45.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>There are no wineries in SA, but within 1 hour there are many. However, the majority of grapes are 7+ hours from here, if not CA or OR.</p>\n<p>The best TX white wine I have had is by these folks and they do a very nice tasting: <a href=\"http://www.kuhlmancellars.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">http://www.kuhlmancellars.com/</a>  Their reds are Sonoma County.</p>",
